%evaṃ saṃsārasya svātmanaḥ bhedaṃ dūrīkṛtya  ekānta    darśanaṃ        jñānayogaḥ    \U1
%evaṃ saṃsāra....svātmanoḥ bhedaṃ dūrīkṛtyaṃ ekye?     darśanaṃ        jñānayoga     \U2
